data.name: Tab.Home.SidebarPane.Module.Content.3.Text
data.value: The flagship downhill bike from Awesome Cycles is finally avaliable!

data.name: Tab.Home.LeftPane.Module.Content.4.Text
data.value: Introducing the new line up of Awesome Cycles for 2013. We have brought more new bikes to our line up this year. Come and get them!

data.name: Tab.Home.LeftPane.Module.Content.8.Text
data.value: This year Awesome Cycles will make its first appearance at one of the largest mountain bike festivals in the world.

data.name: Tab.Home.ContentpaneLower.Module.Content.1.Text
data.value: Competition ready right out of the box.

data.name: Tab.Home.Contentpane.Module.Content.1.Text
data.value: We make your riding dreams a reality.

data.name: Tab.Home.Contentpane.Module.Content.2.Text
data.value: We love it when we can provide our customers with their dream bicycle. That’s why we have the best and most creative

data.name: Tab.Home.Contentpane.Module.Content.3.Text
data.value: people in the industry on hand to design and build exactly what you want.

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.0.Text
data.value: Our very first shop opened in 2011 in SomePlace,

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.1.Text
data.value: California. We build, sell and ship our bikes worldwide

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.3.Text
data.value: We love it when we can provide our customers with their dream bicycle.

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.4.Text
data.value: That's why we have the best and most creative people in the industry on hand to design and build exactly what you want.

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.5.Text
data.value: The story of Awesome cycles started numerous years ago with two guys, a simple idea and shed in Chris's moms backyard. After hundreds of hours of mindstorming and Will's steady hand with a welder the first awesome cycle was forged out of fire in molten lava that had been blessed by Chuck Norris himself! Just kidding, can you imagine?

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.6.Text
data.value: Today the company has evolved to a level that neither Will nor Chris could have ever imagined.

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.7.Text
data.value: Our bikes are created by some of the most passionate people in the industry. We use only the finest materials to elegantly craft some of the most beautiful bikes the roads and trails have ever seen. The use of modern technologies and practices has helped us achieve being one of the top bicycle brands in the world.

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.8.Text
data.value: We continue to push the limits of what bikes are capable of achieving in the hopes of building a future where our bikes are enjoyed by people the world over.

data.name: Tab.About.Contentpane.AboutUsModule.Content.9.Text
data.value: Isn't it about time you joined the Awesome Cycles family?

data.name: Tab.Products.ContentPane.Module.Content.1.Text
data.value: We are constantly pushing the limits of what bikes are capable of. Through careful testing, evaluation and production practices we can 100% guarantee that our gravity specific bikes will help you push the limits in the ever evolving sport of freeride mountain biking.

data.name: Tab.Products.ContentPane.Module.Content.4.Text
data.value: The mountain is where we at Awesome Cycles like to call home. Whether it’s a short ride through the woods with your family, or an epic all day adventure through some of the toughest terrain. We are sure have the perfect mountain bike for any situation.

data.name: Tab.Products.ContentPane.Module.Content.6.Text
data.value: From the Tour De France to the roads in California our road bikes have done it all. Taking some of the purest materials possible we have developed these modern road bikes to be both strong and amazingly light all without breaking the bank.

data.name: Tab.Products.ContentPane.Module.Content.8.Text
data.value: With the rising cost of gas who has money to commute by car anymore? That is why for 2012 we are proud to launch our new line of city specific bikes. Stylish, affordable and easily customizable our city bikes could be just what you are looking for.

data.name: Tab.Products.ContentPane.Module.Content.10.Text
data.value: This is where it all starts. A kids first bike is one of the greatest gifts you can give to them. With bikes designed to fit kids of all ages, we are sure you can find some thing that they will truly enjoy for many years to come.

data.name: Tab.Products.ContentPane.Module.Content.12.Text
data.value: Our next generation of purpose built street, park and dirt jump machines have arrived. Built out of 100% Chromoly steel our BMX and Hard Tail frames can handle it all.

data.name: Tab.Products.ContentPane.Module.Content.13.Text
data.value: So what are you waiting for?

data.name: Tab.ContactUs.CenterPane.Module.Content.12.Text
data.value: To reach Awesome Cycles by telephone during office hours (Monday-Friday 8:00am-5:00pm PST) please call (650) 288-3150. You can fax us at (650) 288-3191.

data.name: Tab.ContactUs.CenterPane.Module.Content.14.Text
data.value: If you can't find what you are looking for in the lists we have provide hare, please use the contact form to the right and we will respond within 24 hours.

data.name: Tab.ContactUs.LeftPane.Module.Content.14.Text
data.value: Enter postal code or city and country
